name: One In a Million Tee
description:
You stand out.  You are the main attraction.  You are... one in a million.

Let it be known that you're a force to be reckoned with.  Rock the "One in a Million" t-shirt, exclusively from the uGen Collection.

Manufactured and screen-printed locally in California, this is a unique streetwear item that will allow you to do one thing: Define Yourself.

    * 100% fine combed cotton tee with double-rib neckband.
    * White-and-grey permanent print on black.
    * Front reads "I'm one in a million..." above graphic of the 'millionaire man.'
    * uGen logo centered on back.
    * Comes with hand-numbered card of authenticity.
    * 4 sizes available: S, M, L, XL.


LIMITED RUN PRODUCTION: Less than 100 shirts in existence, so get yours NOW!  Limit 2 per customer.
